              {
                "item_values": [],
                "key": "Tutorial",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>These agile warriors may be found in the many scattered mercenary groups that hail from the desert. They will unleash the ominous spirit sealed in their weapons after taking a certain amount of damage to <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">enter an Infused Form</span> that greatly boosts their combat capabilities. Once this Infused Form ends, they will enter a weakened state for a time.</p>"
